# =========================
# Domain Matrix (Cloudflare Pages)
# - Brand:  frontendnext.com
# - Weekly: frontendweekly.cn
# =========================

# 1) Canonicalize weekly content to weekly domain.
https://frontendnext.com/weekly https://frontendweekly.cn/weekly 301
https://frontendnext.com/weekly/* https://frontendweekly.cn/weekly/:splat 301

# 2) Weekly domain only serves weekly section.
https://frontendweekly.cn/ https://frontendweekly.cn/weekly 301
https://frontendweekly.cn/weekly https://frontendweekly.cn/weekly 200
https://frontendweekly.cn/weekly/* https://frontendweekly.cn/weekly/:splat 200

# 3) Any non-weekly path on weekly domain flows back to brand site.
https://frontendweekly.cn/* https://frontendnext.com/:splat 301
